title: Sabrina and Ruben Veliz – Paciencia
description:
Sabrina and Ruben Veliz dance “Paciencia” played live by La Juan D'Arienzo, sung by Fernando Rodas, at Southern California Tango Championship & Festival 2019 in Los Angeles, USA.
